Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Erica has given reason she is in a relationship with Kiddwaya. Erica had chosen to be in a relationship with Kiddwaya instead of Laycon who had interest in her. The BBNaija lockdown lovers have been seen in romantic positions and kissed in the house. However, speaking on Thursday morning with Kiddwaya, Erica said she is just settling for him because she has no other option in the house. According to her, outside the house would be different because she would have options. Erica said: “I’m settling with you right now because I don’t have options “There’s no choice right now, so I’m making use of what I have. “You are a 10 in hotness and maybe friendship aspect, but other aspect you’re 1/10.”